%  of their body weight while a sheep needs 3% of their body weight in grass. <\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_mEnD6f":{"type":"column","settings":{"image_full_width":false,"image_link":"","retina":true,"title":"✔ FREE FROM LANOLIN","text":"<p>Lanolin is a grease found in sheep wool that causes people to itch. It takes toxic chemicals and gallons of hot water to remove it from the fibers. <a href=\"http:\/\/https\/\/armsofandes.com\/blogs\/news\/alpaca-fiber\">Alpaca <\/a>is naturally free from Lanolin. <\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"column_GC7ned":{"type":"column","settings":{"image_full_width":false,"image_link":"","retina":true,"title":"✔ SUSTAINABLE AGRICULTURE","text":"<p>Peruvian farmers use a sustainable approach when farming animals. There are no harsh chemicals involved and carbon footprint is minimal. Alpacas wander freely and are rarely transported by vehicle. <\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["column_cGmGrz","column_mEnD6f","column_GC7ned"],"custom_css":[".backgroundf {margin: 3% 8% 0 8%;}",".rte {font-size:1rem; color:#666666ff!important;}"],"name":"Multicolumn","settings":{"fondo_color":"#ffffff","heading":"","heading_left":false,"heading_color":"#f07f08","heading_weight":700,"heading_size_section":20,"description":"","full_width":true,"display_type":"grid","image_ratio":"adapt","columns_desktop":3,"text_alignment":"left","heading_size":"h5","mobile_swipe":false,"show_progress_bar":true,"disable_top_spacing":true,"disable_bottom_spacing":true}},"gallery_wpfaf9":{"type":"gallery","blocks":{"image_4HdV8g":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/pf-39082e30--IMG5699-1-Edited-1.webp","subheading":"","title":"","text":"","link_label":"SHOP NOW","link":"shopify:\/\/collections\/womens-alpaca-wool-clothing","use_text_button":false,"block_link":"","product_list":[]}},"image_3zjK9m":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/pf-34d7fad7--IMG5698-2-Edited.webp","subheading":"","title":"","t